OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with rain and
OL,6,Fdrizzle. Rain will be heavy and most
OL,7,Fpersistent in the morning, turning
OL,8,Flighter and patchier for a time in the
OL,9,Fafternoon before some heavier
OL,10,Foutbreaks move into the west again
OL,11,Flater. Breezy near coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain. Staying mostly
OL,15,Fcloudy overnight with outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain, but these mostly in the west
OL,17,Fwith clearer spells developing in the
OL,18,Feast. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
